701513f-a.title: Bronx: Mount Eden Avenue - Monroe Avenue
701513f-a.text:
3O1-305 Mt. Eden Ave., at the N.E. corner of Monroe Ave., showing
the Annette Court. The three frame dwellings, on the left, bear numbers
1650 to 1654 Monroe Ave.
About 1929.
Gelles Advertising Agency.
